OL,3,CReform has chosen freedoms of speech
OL,4,Cat universities as one of its
OL,5,Cbattlegrounds
OL,7,FThe university itself has been careful
OL,8,Fto distance itself from the
OL,9,Fcontroversy. It says student societies
OL,10,Foperate independently of the
OL,11,Finstitution, insists it remains
OL,12,Fpolitically neutral, an that it
OL,13,Fsupports freedom of speech. That
OL,14,Fdistinction, however, hasn't stopped
OL,15,Fthe party from announcing a new
OL,16,Fpledge: if elected, it would ban no-
OL,17,Fplatforming at Welsh universities
OL,18,Faltogether.
