OL,7,FAlongside the policy row, questions
OL,8,Fhave also been swirling around
OL,9,FReform's leadership in Wales. New
OL,10,Fleader, Dan Thomas, has faced
OL,11,Fspeculation about whether he is
OL,12,Feligible to stand at all. Senedd
OL,13,Fcandidates must be registered on the
OL,14,Felectoral roll in Wales, and there had
OL,15,Fbeen claims that Thomas lives in Bath
OL,16,Frather than Wales.
