OL,3,CReform has chosen freedoms of speech
OL,4,Cat universities as one of its
OL,5,Cbattlegrounds
OL,7,F"Sadly, too often we see free speech
OL,8,Fstifled in our academic institutions,
OL,9,Fand it's time to change that. Under my
OL,10,Fleadership, Reform UK will introduce
OL,11,Flegislation within the first 100 days
OL,12,Fof forming a government in Wales to
OL,13,Fput an end to the militant cancel
OL,14,Fculture and no-platforming in
OL,15,Funiversities.
OL,17,F"These will be the strongest higher
OL,18,Feducation free speech protections in
OL,19,Fthe United Kingdom. That's real change
OL,20,Ffor Wales."
